name: TKSmartCardATR.InterfaceGroup
desc: A single interface-bytes group for a Smart Card ATR (Answer to Reset).

items.name: var ta: NSNumber?
items.desc: The TA interface byte of ATR group, or nil if TA is not present.

items.name: var tb: NSNumber?
items.desc: The TB interface byte of ATR group, or nil if TB is not present.

items.name: var tc: NSNumber?
items.desc: The TC interface byte of ATR group, or nil if TC is not present.
